    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic classic! It\u2019s in truly good condition, showing the care it has received over the years with a reliable engine and a clean, comfortable interior. While you\u2019ll notice some minor, age-appropriate wear, it remains a wonderful and dependable choice for any enthusiast looking for a well-maintained ride.",
