    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those looking for a major project or a donor vehicle for parts. The exterior has significant damage, including deep scratches, dents, and visible rust on several panels. Mechanically, the car is currently non-operational; the engine requires a complete overhaul, and the transmission is slipping. The interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It will need to be towed from its current location.",
